condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :4342-BEN; 4343MLI; H321-GUI | Description :No later than twelve months after the Effectiveness Date, each ofBenin, Guinea and Mali shall establish its respective National Focal Structure (NFS) with satisfactory composition andattributions. | Due Date :08-Nov-2008

Finance Agreement :4342-BEN; 4343MLI; H321-GUI; 4348-UNI; 4343MLI; | Description :NBA shall furnish to the Association, as soon asavailable, but in any case no later than September 1 of each year, an annual action plan and budget for the Project. | Due Date:21-Jan-2009

Finance Agreement :4342-BEN; 4343MLI; H321-GUI; 4348-UNI;4343MLI; | Description :No later than two months after the EffectivenessDate, NBA shall recruit an accountant and a procurement specialist, each with satisfactory terms of reference, qualifications andexperience. | Due Date :08-Jan-2008

Finance Agreement :4342-BEN; H320-NIR- | Description :No later than two months after the Effectiveness Date, the NationalImplementing Agency of Benin and Niger shall each recruit a procurement consultant with satisfactory qualifications. | Due Date:20-Nov-2007

Finance Agreement :4343MLI; | Description :No later than one month after the Effectiveness Date, Mali#s National ImplementingAgency shall recruit an accountant with satisfactory terms of reference, qualifications and experience. | Due Date :08-Dec-2007

Finance Agreement :4348-UNI | Description :No later than four months after the Effective Date, NBA shall enter into a Memorandum ofUnderstanding with the West African Power Pool for the joint supervision of Component 2 of the Nigeria Project | Due Date:08-Mar-2008

Finance Agreement :4348-UNI | Description :later than one month after the Effective Date, the Nigeria#s National ImplementingAgency shall recruit a consultant to help prepare the bidding documents for the Kainji dam, with terms of reference. | Due Date:08-Oct-2007
